Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Segawa Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.26,0:00:06.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang ingin kulakukan untuk\Nmerebut posisi pemeran utama.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo menikah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.90,0:01:48.84,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Membuat brosur untuk upacara pernikahan?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.30,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.92,0:01:53.88,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kuil kami juga bisa menjadi\Ntempat upacara pernikahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.24,0:01:57.16,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kami sedang ingin memperbarui brosurnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.62,0:01:58.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi salah mengira, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.22,0:02:04.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Pengantin" tak bisa lepas\Ndari kata "tokoh utama".
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kata lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.82,0:02:07.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudku,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.34,0:02:10.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,pengantin di brosur yang akan kita buat,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.82,0:02:13.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita berdualah yang akan memerankannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.72,0:02:16.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(777.6,1015)}Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.74,0:02:20.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak mau?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Foto pernikahanku dan Segawa?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita lakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.44,0:02:31.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita bicarakan ini dengan ibu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.18,0:02:31.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.34,0:02:34.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak boleh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bercanda.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.36,0:02:41.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengadakan upacara pernikahan\Ndenganmu yang sudah punya tunangan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.72,0:02:46.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sedang mengasingkan diri,\Nkau bertobat saja di depan kuil.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Si Inisial U.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuku tahu kalau kau tidak bersalah,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi dia juga setuju\Nmenyembunyikanmu di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.94,0:03:01.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minta izin soal upacara pernikahan\Nmungkin kelewatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf aku tidak bisa membantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku jadi makin bersemangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.56,0:03:06.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perjuangan baru dimulai, Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang membereskan ruangan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.00,0:03:18.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang membereskannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.10,0:03:24.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, silakan beristirahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Sebagai gantinya...\N- Tidak boleh.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.18,0:03:32.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini harusnya dikerjakan\Noleh pegawai paruh waktu kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau malah buat kami repot.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.04,0:03:40.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya juga sudah selesai\Nmengepel lantai lorong.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hargai niatmu itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi Hiro sudah punya tunangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.68,0:03:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih gagal, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.32,0:03:55.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku minta maaf atas ketidakberdayaanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perjuangan masih panjang, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah menyerah?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.36,0:04:04.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ibumu sudah menolak dengan tegas...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama ini selalu begitu, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski terus-terusan kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau bisa menang di akhir,\Nkau pemenangnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.14,0:04:20.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa bisa seperti sekarang karena\Nterus berhadapan dengan ibunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.06,0:04:28.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Laki-laki bernama Umino\Nyang sebegitunya memengaruhi Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa sebenarnya dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang akan urus!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa memang beda.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, hei, hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau yang bernama Umino?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu benar...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa Anda?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Adu sumo denganku!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.62,0:05:05.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau menang dariku,\Nkuizinkan upacara pernikahannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersiaplah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keadaan macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus kuladeni.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.70,0:05:29.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeblos.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, tidak.\NAku mana kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah! Kau lulus!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kenapa?\N- Kau berhasil!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bravo! Bravo!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sumo bukan soal menang kalah saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.18,0:05:48.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyali yang kau tunjukkan ketika\Nberani melawanku tadi itu hebat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menyukaimu, Umino!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.90,0:05:56.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak kusangka akan tiba waktunya\Naku mandi dengan ayahnya Segawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.82,0:06:02.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua hal ini terjadi pada Hiro\Nkarena kedatanganku ke kuil ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dan ibunya
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,menikah karena saling bertunangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi itu yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.12,0:06:15.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kuil ini memiliki\Nsejarah selama 1300 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti ada alasan tertentu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu aku masuk ke kuil ini sebagai menantu,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketika aku berumur 23 tahun,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.06,0:06:27.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,sedangkan Asami 21 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat pertama kali bertemu,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.10,0:06:33.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku langsung berpikir\Nakan betapa cantiknya dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.16,0:06:37.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada sesuatu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.08,0:06:42.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.38,0:06:47.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan menikah dengan pria sebesar ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah menikah pun,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.14,0:06:58.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku melalui masa di mana perasaan\Nsepihakku ini tak kunjung terbalas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda melalui banyak kesulitan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan salah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku justru bahagia\Nbisa bersama orang sebaik dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.56,0:07:12.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itulah, aku ingin Hiro\Nbebas menikahi orang yang ia sukai.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.02,0:07:13.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.42,0:07:18.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asami pasti menikahiku\Nkarena ingin melindungi kuil ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku yakin dia masih\Nmenyesal sampai sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku bukan tunangannya...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.46,0:07:28.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin ia sudah jalani hari-harinya\Ndengan bahagia sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selalu beranggapan begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah!\NWaktu mandi selesai!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.72,0:07:35.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.54,0:07:42.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Roti yakisoba...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Umino!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.56,0:07:48.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa-bisa kau demam jika\Nkau biarkan roti yakisobamu nongol!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekalipun ayah setuju, Ibu tidak demikian.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.72,0:08:05.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau buat brosur seperti itu,\Nbagaimana kau akan temui tunanganmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.02,0:08:10.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan menikah dengan tunanganku!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bilang begitu lagi...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa alasanmu menolak sedemikian keras?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.10,0:08:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku mengerti\Nsetelah melihat Ibu dan Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menikah dengan tunangan pun
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak menjamin akan bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ap-?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.12,0:08:32.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku tidak bisa bahagia,\Nkenapa aku harus menikah?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.04,0:08:36.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanpa menikah pun,\Naku bisa melindungi kuil!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bicara seenaknya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.36,0:08:41.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apanya yang kau maksud dengan "mengerti"?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibulah yang tidak mengerti!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau kau izinkan saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asami!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengambilan foto upacara pernikahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu cuma rekayasa!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami tidak sedang membahas itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.26,0:08:55.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, kau juga bermasalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.96,0:08:58.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.98,0:09:02.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau cuma menang besar saja,\Ntapi tidak bisa apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasang kancing baju saja tidak bisa,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,suka merusak barang,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,- "Kaus kakinya robek sendiri."\N- sejauh ini berapa pasang
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,kaus kaki yang telah kau robek?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum lagi, soal atap kuil\Nyang kau hancurkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak-anak yang berkunjung pun\Nkau buat menangis.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.88,0:09:22.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak ada aku,\Nkau hanya bisa bersumo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sumo?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.26,0:09:24.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah, bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.12,0:09:25.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu juga harus tahan!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya, bilang saja ayah\Nsekadar tak bisa urus diri sendiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah itu adalah suatu bukti?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.84,0:09:38.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.62,0:09:44.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu membuktikan kalau Ibu Segawa\Nsenantiasa berada di sisi Ayahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.28,0:09:48.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia begitu memperhatikan\Ndan mengerti soal suaminya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak akan begitu\Nkalau dia membenci ayahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.48,0:09:58.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah itu menunjukkan betapa\NIbumu mencintai Ayahmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.92,0:10:04.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan kebarat-baratan\Nmenggunakan kata "cinta" begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai menangis?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah... Jangan menangis.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.64,0:10:14.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.16,0:10:16.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.12,0:10:19.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa tahu soal sisi lain keluargaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuku
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,awalnya tidak menyukai ayahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia perlahan jatuh hati, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.94,0:10:27.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.34,0:10:32.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkat kehadiranmu yang singkat,\Naku jadi tahu akan hal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kita menikah,\Nmungkin aku akan tahu lebih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bercanda, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bercanda?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,apakah akhirnya aku
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,bisa bebas jatuh cinta?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,alasan mereka menikah\Ntidak ada hubungannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama mereka bahagia sekarang,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,bukankah itu yang terpenting?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya, jika mereka awalnya bukan\Ntunangan pun tidak masalah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini, Umino...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.26,0:11:14.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik! Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.72,0:11:18.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, kalian berdua!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berubah pikiran!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.28,0:11:25.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menikahlah dengan tunanganmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini aku kembali tersadar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahwa menikah dengan tunangan\Nmemang yang paling membahagiakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Apa yang kau bicarakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu, tolong bantu aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang benar apa yang dia katakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.20,0:11:47.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan begitu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.14,0:12:01.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Upacara pernikahan...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya kita dapat restu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh! Kau berhasil.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini berkatmu, Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku melakukan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.10,0:12:16.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuku tampaknya masih tidak terima.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.02,0:12:22.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayahku meyakinkan ibuku karena\Ningin melihatku pakai baju pengantin.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.92,0:12:25.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, ayo kita tancap gas.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata aku memang tidak berbuat apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Film dokumentasi pertumbuhan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku pernikahan
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.02,0:12:38.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,juga dirayakan untuk keluarga\Nyang membesarkan mempelai.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.24,0:12:43.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuharap dengan ini pihak keluarga\Nbisa mengenang masa lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.52,0:12:49.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa juga ada masa seperti ini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya pasti ada, lah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.14,0:12:56.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu waktu aku menerima\Npenghargaan di festival olahraga SD.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kau terobsesi\Njadi yang terbaik dari dulu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.94,0:13:06.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau ternyata memang mencintai kuil ini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bisa tahu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raut wajahmu beda saat di luar kuil.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.96,0:13:20.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.68,0:13:24.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino, kau cocok sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa iya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.14,0:13:31.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku jadi gugup kalau\Nsudah pakai baju pengantin.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita benar-benar akan\Nadakan upacara pernikahan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau cuma bohongan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak rapi, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kira-kira apa maksudnya "itu"?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu di sekolah...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak sengaja.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada maksud apa-apa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.92,0:14:08.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setiap ciuman pasti memiliki makna.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menantikan hari H-nya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ciuman ikrar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senang kalian ke Kedai Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah tentukan pesanan Anda?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.66,0:14:28.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kami salah masuk lapak?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengenalmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau putri dari Raja Hotel itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.78,0:14:40.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin tambah pengalaman sosial,\Njadi aku kerja paruh waktu di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebetulan sedang kekurangan orang,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami jadi terbantu berkat kedatangan Erika.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.22,0:14:50.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia cekatan, pelanggan juga menyukainya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.76,0:14:53.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi yang senior di sini,\Njangan sampai tersalip!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei! Cuciannya masih numpuk, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidakkah kau lambat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang kulakukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini...\NMulutmu saja yang bekerja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.38,0:15:09.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau jadi lembek karena\Nlama tak bantu pekerjaan kedai?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi, jangan terlalu dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.96,0:15:18.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku baru kali ini\Nhabiskan waktu di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.34,0:15:21.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka jadi berlebihan memujiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malahan, tadi aku menumpahkan bir.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga sudah pecahkan lima piring.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.92,0:15:28.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hehe.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.20,0:15:31.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bagaimana sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.84,0:15:37.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau murung karena kepikiran itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi, kau imut sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan cuma soal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.74,0:15:48.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi pasti jalani hari dengan tegar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.38,0:15:54.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski kami berduaan di hotel,\Ndia cuma peduli soal belajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin dia diskusi pelajaran\Ndengan Hiro sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.90,0:16:02.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu, tidak ada\Nsesuatu di antara kalian?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu "sesuatu"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada apa-apa, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Sachi!\NAmbil koran sore dari kotak pos!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Undangan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Undangan untuk Ai?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Undangan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.32,0:16:36.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Kami berdua akan\Nmenggelar upacara pernikahan."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.48,0:16:37.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Mohon hadir pada acara kami."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Umino Nagi."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Segawa Hiro."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.78,0:16:43.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang tadi cuma bercanda.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.42,0:16:50.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami mohon kerja sama Anda\Nsebagai model tamu untuk pemotretan
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.64,0:16:53.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,foto brosur pernikahan kuil.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.16,0:16:55.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami tunggu kehadiran Anda.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.26,0:16:57.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus sekali, Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Logonya kelihatan cocok.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.30,0:17:05.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi gugup, jadi tolong henti...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kecantikanmu tak ada yang menandingi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.16,0:17:28.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar, kau terlalu berlebihan, Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.96,0:17:33.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat... Segawa terlalu cantik.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.46,0:17:34.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sampai terdiam.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh! Kenapa ini?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fokusnya blur semua!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu karena kau menangis.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ambil foto dengan benar saja tak bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang kau ini cuma bisa bersumo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sumo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingat kalau Ibu masih belum merestui.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.10,0:17:50.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua, berdirilah di depan kuil.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino, lebih dekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.72,0:17:59.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena ini pernikahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memanggilmu "Umino" jadi aneh.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi, kau terlalu malu-malu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.24,0:18:14.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini? Gokil!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ala Jepang sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku salah baju?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Amano?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Erika!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau datang, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hiro, kau cantik sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,kenapa pakai gaun putih?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Tidak boleh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.06,0:18:32.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Putih itu warna buat pengantin!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf banget, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupikir ini cuma pesta biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa, yang tadi lucu bagimu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi rasanya bagus juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Upacara pernikahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin menggelarnya suatu saat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin datang\Nke upacara pernikahanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.06,0:18:55.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Datang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan siapa kalian\Nmembayangkan pernikahan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mempelai mohon ke ruang tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus tunggu di sini, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah siapkan kejutan di sesi tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.80,0:19:11.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepada para tamu undangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.32,0:19:16.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah datang ke upacara\Npernikahan bohongan hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.24,0:19:20.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sementara hadirin berbincang,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mochizuki Ai.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan unjuk gigi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.86,0:19:28.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia muncul lebih mencolok\Ndaripada si pengantin!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak akan kubiarkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dilarang menyerobot duluan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat dilarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malah nyanyi lagu kecemburuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami cuma ambil foto,\Njadi tak perlu nyanyi...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.80,0:19:47.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai ini orangnya tak bisa biarkan\Nsesuatu yang setengah-setengah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.92,0:19:51.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sesi selanjutnya,\Naku akan menyanyi untuk Nagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai ketika berdiri di panggung...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Auranya luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.10,0:20:02.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Upacaranya mau mulai, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.00,0:20:12.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Upacaranya ternyata diadakan\Ndi tempat sembahyang, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya jadi tegang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, di mana Sachi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, kalau itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ada ujian tahun ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula aku tidak tertarik.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini ada simulasi ujian katanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.76,0:20:29.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengantin pria dan wanita memasuki ruangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus, Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.58,0:20:42.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau cantik! Persis seperti\NAsami waktu muda.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.02,0:20:45.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal cuma upacara pernikahan bohongan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tetap saja gugup, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.86,0:20:51.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktunya telah tiba.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini Segawa
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah pemeran utamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku yang berdiri di sampingnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,silakan ciuman ikrar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Sungguh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengikuti pernikahan ala era Reiwa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.92,0:21:18.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang seperti apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.16,0:21:23.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang rasanya akan ada yang kurang\Nkalau tidak lakukan itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai tidak terima.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.82,0:21:30.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi, bukankah matanya memerah?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.38,0:21:33.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak tahan lihatnya walau ini bohongan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.80,0:21:39.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suatu saat,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.46,0:21:43.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,apakah akan datang
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.68,0:21:50.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,hari seperti ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.98,0:22:00.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan rebut Kakak dariku!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.98,0:22:03.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.77,0:23:38.12,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Musuh sebenarnya adalah Sachi...
